{"tid":262502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實成日遲到嘅人係咩心態","createTime":"2017-05-29T09:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T10:53:44.000Z","uid":943,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c43b3de66a766fb05343de7e8bc226533301eb52","tid":262502,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"其實你都廿幾歲人啦<br />\n時間都控制唔好<br />\n最衰係聽到啲:吓？遲到基本嘢啦，邊有人準時<br />\n明知要遲到仲meme麼麼<br />\n話咩當你係朋友先會遲到咋，你嬲就即係冇當我係朋友啦<br />\n其實準時係對人最基本嘅尊重嚟，你約我又遲到，你有冇尊重過我？<br />\n成日大條道理遲到真係好討厭<br />\n你要遲到，咁我約實你時間有咩用？<br />\n仲要你嬲佢遲到佢會覺得你好小器<br />\n大佬你唔係遲十分鐘，你係半個鐘起跳喎<br />\n<br />\n睇唔過眼啲人遲到仲聲大大，好乞人憎"},{"pid":"dd2d25f2767e307ed8dac6e167eba64e1122f74e","tid":262502,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:44:44.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲人唔好咁玻璃心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610a4949687d9c350607dd6f7ebb4ea22baf971c","tid":262502,"uid":17426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"好撚憎人遲到"},{"pid":"3e33f0994a9326da7c9755beba19d2d05d58ac66","tid":262502,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚憎人遲到</blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁憎"},{"pid":"1f2d84b14ee852011e597fa7a24803cc5989a3f6","tid":262502,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廿幾歲人唔好咁玻璃心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做錯嘢但話人玻璃心"},{"pid":"7156575fbd6e710ac3e633aaf45ae6d2eee1b56d","tid":262502,"uid":44301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"先唔理朋友<br />\n女朋友遲到講到天經地義咁<br />\n唔係話唔等你，但起